SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A, OLVWS_AVAILABLE_PRODBR V WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = V.PRODUCT_CODE AND V.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.MODULE = 'FT' AND A.PRODUCT_START_DATE <= GLOBAL.APPLICATION_DATE AND ((A.PRODUCT_END_DATE IS NULL) OR A.PRODUCT_END_DATE > GLOBAL.APPLICATION_DATE) ORDER BY PRODUCT_CODE

SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME, NULL RES_TRN_CODE FROM STTM_CORE_BRANCH A WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_BRANCH_PARAMETERS B WHERE A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND B.MODULE_CODE = GLOBAL.FN_GET_MODULE_ID) ORDER BY BRANCH_CODE
